      <title>世间皆苦，唯有自渡</title>
      <link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E4%B8%96%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%86%E8%8B%A6-%E5%94%AF%E6%9C%89%E8%87%AA%E6%B8%A1/</link>
